# Exercise 5: Documenting Headers

## Headers
**Name** | **Description** | **Required** | **Values**
--- | --- | --- | ---
Content-Type | format for the photo | Optional | Valid values: `image/jpeg`, `imgage/png`, `image/gif`.  Default is `image/jpeg`.
Accept | format for return data | Optional | Valid values: `application/json`, `application/xml`.  Default is `application/json`.
<br/>

## Sample Request  

**POST /photo**  
https://phantasticFoto.com/api/v1/photo  
<br/>

**Headers**
```
Content-Type: image/png
Accept: application/xml
```
<br/>

**Request body**
```

```
<br/>

This requests uploads a photo in PNG format (encoded in Base64) and returns data in XML format.
